# <Portfolio_Website>

## Description

Built a responsive Portfolio Website that can showcase the skills and talent to employers by using flexbox, media, and CSS variables......

Portfolio_Website mock-up

-Corresponding navigation.

-Presenting the developer's name, projects, contact information, etc.

-Project images will show bigger and moving when you click or hover them, you can click the link to see more details.

-Presenting with a responsive layout that adapts to various screens and devices.

